{% extends "layout/citizen-authenticated.njk" %}
{% from "govuk/components/inset-text/macro.njk" import govukInsetText %}

{% set mainClasses = "app-container govuk-body" %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Privacy notice</h1>

      <p class="govuk-body">The ‘Victim pathfinder: Track my case’ service is provided by the Ministry of Justice (MoJ). The MoJ is committed to the protection and security of your personal information.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">It is important that you read this privacy notice so that you are aware of how and why we are using such information.</p>

      <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What data we collect</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body">We collect and use the following information:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>your email address</li>
        <li>questions, queries or feedback you enter and save, including your email address if you decide to leave feedback or volunteer to participate in post-beta usage research sessions</li>
        <li>your Internet Protocol (IP) address, and details of which <a class="govuk-link" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/help/browsers">web browser</a> you used</li>
        <li>information on how you use the site, <a class="govuk-link" href="/cookies">using cookies</a> and page tagging techniques</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What we do with your data</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body">No information that you provide will be shared outside the MoJ, other than with MoJ IT providers that provide services supporting the running of this service.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">We will not:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>sell or rent data to third parties</li>
        <li>share data with third parties for marketing purposes</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="govuk-body">Most of the personal information we use to:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>allowing your access to the service for private beta</li>
        <li>contact you if you sign up to take part in user research</li>
        <li>understand the performance of the service</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="govuk-body">Where you provide your consent, we use <a class="govuk-link" target="_blank" href="https://support.google.com/analytics/topic/2919631">Google Analytics</a> cookies to collect information about how you use Track My Case. This includes IP addresses.</p>

      <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Contact us or make a complaint</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body">Contact us if you:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>have a question about anything in this privacy notice</li>
        <li>think that your personal data has been misused or mishandled</li>
      </ul>

