        SK9 5AF<br><br>
        Telephone: 0303 123 1113<br>
        ICO website: <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.ico.org.uk" target="_blank">https://www.ico.org.uk</a>
      </p>

      <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Changes to this policy</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body">We may change this privacy notice. In that case, the ‘last updated’ date at the bottom of this page will also change. Any changes to this privacy notice will apply to you and your data immediately.</p>

      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Date of last update</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body">15 December 2025</p>
